reviewText: A silly, but fun b movie that stars Dan Haggerty as a repo man who is also a karate expert and race car visionary. If you like camp and cheese, worth a look. I mean, group freestyle rap sessions.

This film was a true humdinger, in the Dan Haggerty tradition.  I quite enjoyed the story, the action, the acting, the direction, the scenery, the score, the editing, the mise en scene, how else can I say it?!  Its a humdinger!  Enjoy.

The product was as described I would purchase from the buyer again . Although the content of this video was unique to say the least . Too bad Dan Haggerty has the talent , but not the budget of good Producers or editers  behind him .
